{"tid":1746361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區選要贏就唔該放棄鍵戰","createTime":"2019-11-22T17:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T13:48:58.000Z","uid":89160,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"40bc9f9e07e38049f5b0647491e24dd3e7299bc5","tid":1746361,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:08:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">首先，我唔覺得香港任何選舉對本地政治有任何影響，你去投票香港唔會「向民主踏前一步」，唔好FF，亦唔會強求大家去投。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">但可以幾肯定講，區選結果會影響國際戰線，歐美或多或少視今次係香港人表態，佢地跟進既力度有幾大，區選結果會有影響</span></strong>，但並非致命影響。<br />\n<br />\n首先，你要有心理準備「非建制」唔會大贏，持平小勝已經可以開香檳，地區選舉同口講口賠既「民意調查」並不一樣，佢反對警暴都可以唔投票。<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">調整好你既心理狀態之後，你都仲覺得要幫區選助戰，咁就唔該你放棄鍵戰，平面、網絡文宣已經唔夠時間做，冇時間入腦，你要做既，係用你既 Network 去拉人投票，唔係 WhatsApp 拉票，而要上門拉人去票站，「同儕壓力」強過圖文 100 倍。打晒你phone book 入面所有既電話，朋友拉朋友，當然藍絲可以慳返。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n家陣想贏多少少係得呢個方法。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e078e85281c51dce69cd52a76e97b83cdb32830","tid":1746361,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed26c8e9fecd0b6a476cd28688378fad40d7c10","tid":1746361,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:10:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8667641fbab522c2ab1924ac84dec582dec2a98b","tid":1746361,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421ba65cd349b3c6c73d64d4526e30baf2212f29","tid":1746361,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8354a3aca06bd47c7e96f92afcfb8026ad13173e","tid":1746361,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d90afe9658862fd42de5cb6fab9fcd0ad61332","tid":1746361,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620932d8dc9545c3ac966061fc39cde30d1ef7a2","tid":1746361,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:21:11.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1746369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1746369</a>"},{"pid":"7af79f6444818a31ec36b9534fcd0539817f178e","tid":1746361,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:26:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3d4656ee9411d8501e99b014a12f0a02baab91c8","tid":1746361,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T17:32:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">同場加映，王慧麟評論：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n前輩教落，選舉好講個勢。<br />\n候選人落到區派嘢，就會知道有冇個勢會贏。<br />\n好簡單：出面封晒路。朝早巴士站有一班人排緊隊。候選人一邊播「榮光」，一邊派單張。果d街坊，西口西咁望住你。<br />\n咁就會明白，乜嘢叫做勢。<br />\n咁死啦，西口西面。<br />\n老實：問過一些候選人。<br />\n佢地唔係好樂觀。<br />\n當然，佢地唔會響臉書上承認，形勢麻麻，咁即係認輸啦。<br />\n但係，咁亦唔代表，成日要打飛機，講乜嘢翻盤呀、大贏呀、光復呀、公投呀。<br />\n依家太多自我陶醉的廢話。<br />\n必須承認：其實形勢麻麻，希望大家真係盡量落街投票。<br />\n贏唔到就贏唔到啦。<br />\n支持手足，唔代表要投票支持泛民候選人，兩樣嘢唔係因果，亦唔係掛勾的。呢d係基本邏輯。<br />\n唔好再打飛機認屎認屁了。"},{"pid":"62058e8fa06ee2ae7b7e0945c8f05969b2f35cb8","tid":1746361,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T18:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9729023c8672fad6439ba4b1ca76e0a35af80344","tid":1746361,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808e3cf0830044cc6435038f58c460dfe148319a","tid":1746361,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:48:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}